  "Temperature has no effect on equilibrium": "",
  "Low temperature increases K": "",
  "Although lower temperature favors NH3 (exothermic reaction), it makes the reaction too slow. The compromise at ~450 C provides a reasonable rate with an iron catalyst.": "",
